_pro_VPavic_0001.jpg 2400w" src="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2700x1800/2400x1600/filters:focal(1350x900:1351x901):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25255185/246965_vision_pro_VPavic_0001.jpg" decoding="async" data-nimg="responsive" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/></span><div class="duet--media--caption pt-6 font-polysans-mono text-12 font-light leading-130 tracking-1"> <cite class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline not-italic text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-63 [&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a:hover]:shadow-underline-gray [&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray-63 dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:text-gray-bd dark:[&amp;&gt;a]:shadow-underline-gray">Photo by Vjeran Pavic / The Verge</cite></div></figure></div></div></div></div><div class="relative md:mx-auto md:flex md:max-w-container-md lg:max-w-none"><div class="duet--article--article-body-component-container clearfix sm:ml-auto md:ml-100 md:max-w-article-body lg:mx-100"><div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph mb-20 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">I paid a lot of money for the privilege of getting an <a href="/24054862/apple-vision-pro-review-vr-ar-headset-features-price">Apple Vision Pro</a> brand-new in February. All-in, with optical inserts and taxes, I financed a little over $3,900 for the 256GB version of the headset. A day or so ago, I made a mistake that I’m sure many early adopters are familiar with: I looked up how much it’s been selling for on eBay. </p></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph mb-20 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">On Wednesday, a 1TB Vision Pro, complete with all the included gear, Apple’s fluffy $200 travel case, $500 AppleCare Plus, and claimed to have been “worn maybe about an hour” <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F395354897819%3Fitmmeta%3D01HWGCFBZMJ0SMHV81YWCF4VPY%26hash%3Ditem5c0cfcfd9b%3Ag%3AxxAAAOSwXzNmJYLQ%26itmprp%3Denc%3AAQAJAAAA4GdSx1qmkz%2BdV5kBlmFYjveugKs83qituh46m53pdiWjU%2FX7GFflniGeaxMlsfO1x4L7poRKzFIzFbsMo2U8eHbl7vYhTAjMljFDJplR1HwIftgC4b4teFsyqTmoF81u6AWRxpu%2B%2FUNN428u4%2FE44759y1MDka1g2B%2B3Pnx6Ybi2aVjdyHXeZZ%2B%2BuLhh6v1pEdFIrlfV6fYqPZF9D5dUQ2V3ZAw0T5JOQeq1RyZI%2BLDpsjvRZ0SGbdmCNjnV6xVJIbyOWE8F1YFI%2Fm8zdyHN3NclEH0tjZLVyaAf4p96ttoo%257Ctkp%3ABk9SR_C_vYzkYw%26LH_Auction%3D1">sold for $3,200</a> after 21 bids. The listed shipping estimate was $20.30. Brand new, that combination is $5,007.03 on Apple’s site for me. Another eBay listing, this one with my headset’s configuration (but sans optical inserts) <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F204751348348%3Fitmmeta%3D01HWGCFBZMX320SY11TSWCT1NR%26hash%3Ditem2fac21a27c%3Ag%3AnGEAAOSw2l1mBaL6%26itmprp%3Denc%3AAQAJAAAAwB7D8JgLF5MVpJOx7DfljqrIzB157mbrkGIzoIcKNA%2BH7o1dZsc3rNOfNT9ZpxdQe%2BxyOlik%2B2Ie2coVqOQ%2FzUjqK94LToviN1ArFmznlfiNfULcHWn7mORcXtSkHzHhMGLW8CcgOGw7yl4xHRSPtrels8vASmiWe%2FkFuhsIBK%2FFrxOSat2xMpe0ub2P42z4kYbVkfbHRqsdvwp2rFj7--2e9IyRTNqcQHKgGF3lSqCtSt1P7cYKfvS2YvnGkR37MQ%253D%253D%257Ctkp%3ABk9SR_C_vYzkYw%26LH_Auction%3D1">went for just $2,600</a> — again with most, if not all, of the included accessories. Several other <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F404929468850%3Fitmmeta%3D01HWGCFBZM976AK3FH8W75F3TP%26hash%3Ditem5e47ad59b2%3Ag%3AtYMAAOSwlVNmICfo%26itmprp%3Denc%3AAQAJAAAA4LS0HtX%2BZUS0wGZwCflIJ0Or4mooICpUwSVfM1I%2Fh7KlW39YgRsErgr%2FhTmijAiOPt5cjMH9rSvTqxIFrlGLkAwoFHXoi2ep3DyknaKVM0nOvWv6ll4cJ%2BoCr%2B8eDkxgRDHNP8M89QuieTS6v%2Fj2g%2Fw0WTqfTlavHRlkqPF3LHiSAeERed6O8VplFTJ4WsqrdW5nYeKPfbQybJlE%2B6kE%2BVO8inobu0OgqoWTEJudZl0xtctBTNbMiy8KZLJAQUmFko4Rk9Y%2Bz5d6ZuyaUgpFx4rqpWnhXSQuhg13NFcFvIQJ%257Ctkp%3ABk9SR_C_vYzkYw%26LH_Auction%3D1">256GB</a> and <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F375391428620%3Fitmmeta%3D01HWGCFBZMKXWF0HQVSANWZ9B1%26hash%3Ditem576712a00c%3Ag%3AOC0AAOSwjBVmJ-T5%26itmprp%3Denc%3AAQAJAAAAwPQno9IJpBIaVje6ZBR0lYq295IlbRShHmIbdV71EjcwIWWHdDtPdiAYP%2F2wGhalfveiijsJYCFfuwVJbtTEg7%2Fihtcl7TQzMVlV3c2X41DmXuejyMSAgr7GKm3jmvCKoBXKBV6dqI2gFgE7QH5ohIz3Xqolb7MtWsPshmW6gMD5YvcLWsFwFif%2FI1mBduk%2Fr%2Fqz5ureHZOSsgDkSZnbSoz68EUVemHsX9gTG9yVax%2FTUxzdBPLoU7IDAx7MjK7qaQ%253D%253D%257Ctkp%3ABk9SR_C_vYzkYw%26LH_Auction%3D1">512GB</a> <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2FApple-Vision-Pro-256GB-And-Travel-Case-Bundle-S-S-21W%2F326092309268%3Fnordt%3Dtrue%26orig_cvip%3Dtrue%26rt%3Dnc%26_trksid%3Dp2349526.m43663.l10137">models</a> <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&xs=1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F335350292288%3Fitmmeta%3D01HWGCFBZMTQ0FJK8HQF09CZE3%26hash%3Ditem4e146f5f40%3Ag%3AD3IAAOSwgodmEZ1H%26itmprp%3Denc%3AAQAJAAAA4GfmYgTVwdMpMOCyHIRjfgcioAeldR9XPgwrFodv0UPLuuxauM3wQ8vPCEfLTGVoSHCE%2BQi7PgB8J6LEwAnari9T0eWlLqJFSJKpc3kh2qqPJ244iadpVkMIpTFwodOOzj9oZO2YXHdrnMXIvXTFs%2FnNpugY7MLNG9gkELX5KgfYqF7WA2h6uSD%2B3XfkInB32VOMj%2B0rd